          "date": "2015-11-20 18:44:58.000000000",
          "tz": -480
        },
        "subject": "LU-0000 osc: identify pages pinned for bulk",
        "message": "LU-0000 osc: identify pages pinned for bulk\n\nAdding cl_page::cp_pinned to track pages if they are pinned\nfor bulk transfer. Also, if a page is being held for bulk transfer,\nit shouldn't be reclaimed by OSC LRU.\n\nA policy is added to handle those pinned pages. In ll_releasepage(),\nif the page is currently pinned by bulk, a sync request will be sent\nto OST to commit the transaction. Syncing a single object shouldn't\nbe a problem for ldiskfs and it will be good for ZFS also after zil\nis in place.\n\nunstable_stats under LLITE is removed.\n\nunstable check still exists under OSC only statistic purpose.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I4f4d1ca9520bb44a15a4dc7fef568846a9ab944b\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
